# Sentiment Analysis with BERT  
*Classifying Twitter sentiment using HuggingFace Transformers*  

## Overview  
- Fine-tuned a BERT model for sentiment analysis (positive/negative) with **85% accuracy** on 10k+ tweets.  
- Deployed via FastAPI for real-time text processing.  

## How to Run  
1. Install: `pip install transformers torch`  
2. Run: `python predict.py`  

## Dataset  
[Twitter Sentiment Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/kazanova/sentiment140)  
